dcterms:description: The CCA-LT dataset was captured by a whole-slide scanning machine. The specimens are prepared by Thinprep Cytology Test method with H&E staining to give the image resolution of about 80000×60000 pixels. The dataset is divided into training-validation set and test set (7:3). The training-validation set is overlap-cropped for data augmentation, while the test set is not. Then we crop each whole slide digital image into patches of 512×512 pixels for training.
dcterms:title: CCA-LT dataset
